<title>USA: National Health to set special dividend.</title>
<headline>National Health to set special dividend.</headline>
<dateline>MURFREESBORO, Tenn. 1996-10-17</dateline>
<text>
<p>National Health Investors Inc said Thursday that it intends to pay a special dividend of $0.10 to $0.15 to stockholders of record on November 29.</p>
<p>The company said that paid penalties from several companies and successful reinvestment of prepayment proceeds allowed the opportunity to distribute earnings to stockholders.</p>
<p>The exact amount will be finalized November 18.</p>
<p>The dividend will be payable on February 10.</p>
